localized.description:

Youtube will not last life long
If all the videos are gone
From a little stupid rule
All of this happening just ain't cool
I thought it was a place for fun
Entertainment for everyone
Now these companies are barging in
Tearing up the site like it belongs to them
Threatening Youtube for having their songs
Can't we all just get along?

Almost everything on their site

localized.description:
Parody of all those University commercials that try and get you to come to their school... Except this time, they're gonna be honest with you!
Thank you to everyone who was a part of this video and also..

Shout-out to the University of Nevada, Reno, whose beautiful
campus was shown at :12 into the video. The University of Nevada, Reno is
one of the most affordable national Tier 1 universities (students pay 72
percent less in tuition than kids at other Tier 1 universities), they
graduate with less debt (Nevada is ranked #6 for least student debt), and
Nevada graduates have starting salaries among the highest in the nation.
Oh, yeah, celebrity graduates include Colin Kaepernick of the San
Francisco 49ers and Susan Desmond-Hellman, CEO of the Bill & Melinda Gates
Foundation. So, Go Wolf Pack! and thanks for being good sports and letting

snippet.title: So Damn Stupid!

localized.description:
Again we don't hate soulja boy!!! We only spoof his music because its the best and most popular to spoof!

So Damn Stupid!

Written and Performed by:
Ryan Higa 
Sean Fujiyoshi

Lyrics

Intro:
Hey, I can't understand what the hell hes saying, so I'm gonna write something new for y'all.  Man sometimes his songs are so stupid and it gets on my nerves and I don't want to hear it.  So stupid like DayDeeDay!

Chorus:
(Hey Asian Boy, can I) DayDeeDay
(Yo Sean, I really like your) DayDeeDay
(I made a fart) Daybededay Daybededay
(Hey man, I was just wondering can I get your) DayDayDee.
So Damn Stupid! (Day)
So Damn Stupid! (Day)
So Damn Stupid! (Day)
So Damn Stupid! (DayDay)
So Damn Stupid! (Day)
So Damn Stupid! (Day)
So Damn Stupid! (Day)
So Damn Stupid! (DayDay)

Verse 1:
I wanna ask you Soulja Boy
How the hell you became a star.
You don't even rap or sing,
You just shout its so bizarre.
How you sold so much copies,
That everybody wants to jive.
If everybody thought like me,
You wouldn't even sell five.
And your lucky that you even have
1 fan that wants to talk to you.
(DeeDayDayDee So Stupid DayDayDoo)
This song is so stupid,
That I just want you to know:
Instead of Cranking Dat!
Lets Yank Dat Cameltoe!

Chorus:
(Hey Asian Boy, can I) DayDeeDay
(Yo Sean, I really like your) DayDeeDay
(I made a fart) Daybededay Daybededay
(Hey man, I was just wondering can I get your) DayDayDee.
So Damn Stupid! (Day)

So Damn Stupid! (DayDay)
So Damn Stupid! (Day)
So Damn Stupid! (Day)
So Damn Stupid! (Day)
So Damn Stupid! (DayDay)

Verse 2:
You're a disgrace, this isn't music!
Walking up:
"Soulja boy you make me so damn sick!"
(DayDay)
Don't sing this song, 
Its a piece of crap!
I'm hearing all of this,
And you deserve a slap.
Retire now, might as well give up.
You're popular just like
2 Girls and 1 Cup!
(DeeDayDee)
(DeeDayDee)
(DeeDay, DayDay, DayDay, Day, Aww Debededay)

Chorus:
(Hey Asian Boy, can I) DayDeeDay

snippet.title: Sorry Fans, Blame My A.D.D.

localized.description:
Sorry Fans, Blame My A.D.D.
Written and Performed by Ryan Higa

LYRICS:

As time goes by, I learned that myspace is a great responsibility.
And I realize all the things I haven't done affect all the people around me.
So I wanted to take this time out and apologize for things I haven't done and things that didn't occur yet.
And things I don't want to take responsibility for.

Verse 1

I'm sorry that my friend request have grown
Takes about an hour to approve em alone
I'm sorry for the times that I had to go
You were online and I did not know
That you were at home just waiting for me
To respond to every message and comment I see
I'm sorry for the times I would neglect
I'm sorry for the times that I did not check
I'm sorry for the things I haven't done
I'm a ninja, gangstah, emo, nerd, asian
I'm sorry that I'm busy and always away
I got a lot to do, what more can I say
Cuz I'm doing homework like everyday
I'm sorry that I had to write that fricken essay
I know I didn't take all your request
Like how to be gay or how to be a prep

Bridge 

I understand that you get pissed off 
And its not your fault, I know
All the hate mail I get from you
Just because I respond too slow
I should apologize for singing this song
It sucks and makes a fool out of me
I would respond to you right now
But I'd forget cuz my A.D.D.

Chorus

You can blame my A.D.D.
For me being so busy
Its not that I am lazy
Its just cuz my A.D.D.
Said you can blame my A.D.D.
For me being so busy
Its not that I am lazy

localized.title: Sorry Fans, Blame My A.D.D.

snippet.description:
Sorry Fans, Blame My A.D.D.
Written and Performed by Ryan Higa

LYRICS:

As time goes by, I learned that myspace is a great responsibility.
And I realize all the things I haven't done affect all the people around me.
So I wanted to take this time out and apologize for things I haven't done and things that didn't occur yet.
And things I don't want to take responsibility for.

Verse 1

I'm sorry that my friend request have grown
Takes about an hour to approve em alone
I'm sorry for the times that I had to go
You were online and I did not know
That you were at home just waiting for me
To respond to every message and comment I see
I'm sorry for the times I would neglect
I'm sorry for the times that I did not check
I'm sorry for the things I haven't done
I'm a ninja, gangstah, emo, nerd, asian
I'm sorry that I'm busy and always away
I got a lot to do, what more can I say
Cuz I'm doing homework like everyday
I'm sorry that I had to write that fricken essay
I know I didn't take all your request
Like how to be gay or how to be a prep

Bridge 

I understand that you get pissed off 
And its not your fault, I know
All the hate mail I get from you
Just because I respond too slow
I should apologize for singing this song
It sucks and makes a fool out of me
I would respond to you right now
But I'd forget cuz my A.D.D.

Chorus

You can blame my A.D.D.
For me being so busy
Its not that I am lazy
Its just cuz my A.D.D.
Said you can blame my A.D.D.
For me being so busy
Its not that I am lazy
Its just cuz my A.D.D.


Based on the original song:
Akon - I'm Sorry, Put the Blame On Me

snippet.title: Shed a Tear

localized.description:
For Behind the Scenes / Bloopers go to
http://www.higatv.com

This song is inspired and based off of Far East Movement's new single Rocketeer, go buy their song on Itunes! 
http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/free-wired/id394918462

If you have an extra 99 cents, You can also get our song as well!
http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/shed-a-tear/id404060487?i=404060490&ign-mpt=uo%3D4

Song Written by:
Ryan Higa
Kevin Wu (Kevjumba)

Featuring:
http://www.youtube.com/nigahiga
http://www.youtube.com/chestersee
http://www.youtube.com/kevjumba

All music recorded, mixed, and produced in 1 day by Andy Lange.  See how he does it:
http://youtube.com/andylangemusic

Shot by Scotty Yoshimoto (Go check him out!):
http://www.youtube.com/user/movemediaproductions

Edited by:
Kevin Wu (KevJumba)

Special Thanks to:
Lana Mckissack http://www.youtube.com/LanaMcKissack
Tiffany Daniels http://twitter.com/tiffeesha
Arden Cho http://www.youtube.com/ardenbcho
Ronnie Canupp - Producer http://twitter.com/chronicboom

**LYRICS**
CHORUS:
Here it comes
Can't you see
That we're tough guys and we have feelings.
Take my hand
Close your eyes
With you right here
Imma shed a tear and cry
Don't be afraid to cry cry
You can still be a manly guy guy
Just cry.
Don't be afraid to cry cry
Let it free fall from your eyes eyes

VERSE 1:
Wake up see a sunrise
Let it free fall from your eyes.
Start my day and I read a sonnet
Got got a soft cheek with a tear on it.
Step out and the skies are clear 
I'm a man and I have no fear.
Take a step and I land in crap.
I let it out, no holding back.

(CHORUS)
VERSE 2:
Baby we can go out on a first date.
But you come and pick me up half an hour late.
Girl I'm not gonna lie, that you almost made me cry, 
But I'm a masculine man ill be ok. 
Yeah, your place, toy story 3
the greatest all time kid's movie.
But I forgot, Andy leaves Woody,
And now the tears are coming right back over me.

Find me on: http://www.higatv.com 
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/TheRealRyanHiga 
Myspace: http://www.myspace.com/RyanNigaHiga 
Facebook http://www.facebook.com/higatv

snippet.title: Honk For Japan!

localized.description:
For every 1,000,000 views that this video gets, I will donate another $600.  I will take screenshots again and post on my site http://www.higatv.com for proof, when it happens.

People keep saying "why don't you just donate the money instead of trying to get people to view it?"  My biggest strength right now is that I'm fortunate enough to have a following.  The purpose of this video was not only to support Japan myself, but to encourage others as well. I could have easily donated the money and not made a video about it, but I think its a lot more important to get support from all over the world.  I personally can't donate a million dollars, but if millions of people watch this and decide to chip in, it is possible... I'm just trying to help in the best way that I can.

Money Donated so far: $7275
3/14 - $600 (honk!)
3/16 - $650 (1 million views)
3/17 - $675 (2 million views)
3/19 - $700 (3 million views)
3/24 - $725 (4 million views)
4/2 -   $750 (5 million views)
5/3 -   $775 (6 million views)
7/27 - $800 (7 million views)
1/4/12 - $800 (8 million views) Japan America Society Hawaii

localized.title: Honk For Japan!

snippet.description:
For every 1,000,000 views that this video gets, I will donate another $600.  I will take screenshots again and post on my site http://www.higatv.com for proof, when it happens.

People keep saying "why don't you just donate the money instead of trying to get people to view it?"  My biggest strength right now is that I'm fortunate enough to have a following.  The purpose of this video was not only to support Japan myself, but to encourage others as well. I could have easily donated the money and not made a video about it, but I think its a lot more important to get support from all over the world.  I personally can't donate a million dollars, but if millions of people watch this and decide to chip in, it is possible... I'm just trying to help in the best way that I can.

snippet.title: Ninja Melk

localized.description:
Our homemade epic action/adventure comedy short film about ninjas! Shot on a flipcam. 

If you pause the video and it still doesn't load, refresh the page.  Sometimes it glitches like that.

Note:  Its not our usual type of video, this is our first thats over 6 minutes long, so go easy on us!  I'm glad the majority of you guys like it!  I appreciate all of your kind comments :)

Bloopers are at the end!
And for those of you who keep asking, we did all of the stunts, there were NO stunt doubles.  Tim actually got hurt in that last blooper, but not too bad....  I think.  Ah it was still hilarious!

Lapchung is hidden in one of the scenes that he is not supposed to be in!  If you find him, leave a comment!

snippet.description:
Our homemade epic action/adventure comedy short film about ninjas! Shot on a flipcam. 

If you pause the video and it still doesn't load, refresh the page.  Sometimes it glitches like that.

Note:  Its not our usual type of video, this is our first thats over 6 minutes long, so go easy on us!  I'm glad the majority of you guys like it!  I appreciate all of your kind comments :)

Bloopers are at the end!
And for those of you who keep asking, we did all of the stunts, there were NO stunt doubles.  Tim actually got hurt in that last blooper, but not too bad....  I think.  Ah it was still hilarious!

Lapchung is hidden in one of the scenes that he is not supposed to be in!  If you find him, leave a comment!

snippet.title: Asian Boy - I Miss You Soulja Boy

localized.description:
My apology to Soulja Boy
Parody of Better in Time by Leona Lewis.  After making fun of Soulja Boy's hit song "crank dat" Asian Boy feels bad and wants Soulja Boy Back!


Don't worry no copyrights in here, I made the beat on FL Studio, chilll.

Lyrics:
Asian Boy  I miss you Soulja Boy (All the time)

Intro
Asian boy is back, but this time, hes sad.
Verse 1
I spent long time thinking about you
Thinking of a rap to do
See somehow I cant forget you
I Yank My Cameltoe for you

I am sorry, that I make a song
Making fun of you
It was wrong, I deserve it,
And I realize that I really didnt know (oh oh oh)
The meaning of your music, but I know it now
So please come back to me, cuz I miss you so
All I know is, Im going kiss your phone (or something like that)

Chorus
Thought I crank dat without you
But I cant, I dont know how to (oh yea)
I miss you Soulja Boy all the time
Even though I making fun of you
Its just because I like you (oh yea)
I miss you Soulja Boy all the time 

Verse 2
I couldnt turn off my Youtube
Without trying to do what you do 
The BirdWalk wasnt that easy
So instead I making the BirdSprint  (sprint bird sprint)

If you hear this, contact me
Ill be waiting, in a tree
I believe in
Can you call me before ten
If you didnt notice, youre no ordinary
Boy youre special, in fact youre more
Youre not soulja boy, cuz to me you are soulja man (maaaaaaN) 


Chorus
Thought I crank dat without you
But I cant, I dont know how to (oh yea)
I miss you Soulja Boy all the time
Even though I making fun of you
Its just because I like you (oh yea)
I miss you Soulja Boy all the time

Chorus
Thought I crank dat without you
But I cant, I dont know how to (oh yea)
I miss you Soulja Boy all the time
Even though I making fun of you
Its just because I love you (yes I do)
I miss you Soulja Boy all the time

OooooOooOOooOO
UhhhHhHhHH
Moaning Sounds Are Fun
HeeeeeeEEEeeee
Yeahhheahheahhhhh
OhhhhhHH Yeahhhh
I miss you Soulja Boy

And yes I made the music a little bit louder than my singing.  That was on purpose :) haha
